    "Finally, in [21] the authors implement a multilabel CNN for facial expression recognition and ordinal intensity estimation, highlighting the importance of overcoming interclass variation and employing advanced classification techniques.",
    "In [22], for instance, the authors implemented a neural network-based speech emotion recognition system to classify emotion in a chatbot-a virtual assistant developed to do contact tracing during the COVID-19 pandemic.",
    "In the realm of emotion generation, in [23] the authors introduced an innovative approach using Transformer-based models and emotion-aware attention mechanisms, significantly improving response relevance and emotional expressiveness."
